00:01:19.000 --> 00:01:23.000
The deceleration is constant so the velocity decreases

00:01:23.000 --> 00:01:28.000
by a certain fixed amount of meters per second.

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:32.000
The relationship between velocity and time is linear

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:36.000
and the slope of this line is given by the acceleration.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:41.000
This side has a length of 1, this side has a length of a, the acceleration,

00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:47.000
